  "title": "The Leviathian of Ord Trasi",
  "summary": "On the dead Sith world of Ord Trasi, Grand Admiral Danik Kreldin's expedition, his captive Jedi Johanna, the Mandalorian Master Sergeant Cantrell, the pilot Dareus, and elite 501st stormtroopers, is ambushed at a temple entrance by a Leviathan, a soul-draining Sith abomination that devours and withers trooper after trooper. Blasters prove useless against its hide, and Johanna severs one of its legs with her lightsaber before being battered aside. Unseen by the others, the Sith Darth Malign, haunted by the spectre of his ancestor Palladus, stalks the shadows, bleeding himself to mask his scent and silently testing whether Danik will conquer his fear. Cantrell tosses Johanna a thermal detonator that misses, but on a second attempt the two warriors roll a pair of detonators beneath the beast and blow it apart. With nine of twenty-three troopers left, Danik presses onward up the pyramid and into the crypts toward Davin Keldan's tomb, sending Cantrell and Dareus to scout ahead while keeping the wary Johanna close.",
